464]}], "orig": "Entumoto Private Safari Camp stands levated  in  the  hills  of  a  private  and  secluded scarpment, commanding breathtaking views and sunsets over the Mara plains. Intimate and  Exclusive,  it  is  designed  to  provide  for your total comfort in the heart of Africa. It is on the border of the legendary Masai Mara National Reserve, and with our own conservancy, we are privileged to be part of an arguably,  the  world's  most  spectacular  wildlife sanctuary.", "text": "Entumoto Private Safari Camp stands levated  in  the  hills  of  a  private  and  secluded scarpment, commanding breathtaking views and sunsets over the Mara plains. Intimate and  Exclusive,  it  is  designed  to  provide  for your total comfort in the heart of Africa. It is on the border of the legendary Masai Mara National Reserve, and with our own conservancy, we are privileged to be part of an arguably,  the  world's  most  spectacular  wildlife sanctuary."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/4", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 27.1265, "t": 262.0552146484375, "r": 171.04649999999998, "b": 247.75980555752847, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 16]}], "orig": "WHAT'S ON OFFER?", "text": "WHAT'S ON OFFER?", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/5", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/0"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 27.1265, "t": 236.97011464843752, "r": 259.99809999999997, "b": 225.35509476207392, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 40]}], "orig": "»Walking safaris in our own conservancy.", "text": "»Walking safaris in our own conservancy.", "enumerated": false, "marker": ""}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/6", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/0"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 27.1265, "t": 220.96711464843747, "r": 241.2157, "b": 209.3520947620738