"text": "Entumoto Main Camp", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/16", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 319.9177449, "t": 476.8230146484375, "r": 584.15385333, "b": 405.1999947620738, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 194]}], "orig": "Entumoto Main boasts 4 family tents and 5 double/twin en-suite tents. Each family tent comes equipped with its own en-suite bathroom and toilet, along with a central lounge and a cozy fireplace.", "text": "Entumoto Main boasts 4 family tents and 5 double/twin en-suite tents. Each family tent comes equipped with its own en-suite bathroom and toilet, along with a central lounge and a cozy fireplace."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/17", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 386.8151884, "t": 401.81301464843744, "r": 513.94738765, "b": 390.1979947620738, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 18]}], "orig": "Entumoto Toto Camp", "text": "Entumoto Toto Camp", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/18", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 319.9177449, "t": 386.81101464843744, "r": 584.1322080500001, "b": 330.18999476207375, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 177]}], "orig": "Our  more  budget-friendly  option,  Entumoto Toto,  offers  a  total  of  2  family  tents  and  3 double  en-suites.  Specifically  designed  for families with young children.", "text": "Our  more  budget-friendly  option,  Entumoto Toto,  offers  a  total  of  2  family  tents  and  3 double  en-suites.  Specifically  designed  for families with young children."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/19", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 386.6393205, "t": 326.8030146484374, "r": 514.12596121, "b": 315.1879947620737, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 18]}], "orig": "Entumoto Wild Camp", "text": "Entumoto Wild Camp", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/20", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 319.9177449, "t": 311.80101464843733, "r": 584.1186797500004, "b": 225.17599476207374, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 259]}], "orig": "You  have  the  option  to  stay  in  our  mobile camp, which can be set up at various locations  within  our  conservancy.  This  unique accommodation is  specifically  designed  to cater  to  families  or  groups  consisting  of  a minimum of 4 to 8 people.", "text": "You  have  the  option  to  stay  in  our  mobile camp, which can be set up at various locations  within  our  conservancy.  This  unique accommodation is  specifically  designed  to cater  to  families  or  groups  consisting  of  a minimum of 4 to 8 people."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/21", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 312.2744, "t": 213.6690146484375, "r": 372.0232, "b": 199.37360555752844, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 6]}], "orig": "ACCESS", "text": "ACCESS", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/22", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 319.585, "t": 189.16191464843746, "r": 583.8508706900001, "b": 57.5308947620739, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 380]}], "orig": "You have the choice to reach the camp either by air or by road. If you choose to travel by air, flights  are  from  Wilson  Airport,  offering  a convenient 45-minute journey to Masai Mara.  On  the  other  hand,  if  you  prefer  a scenic adventure, a road safari is available, taking 4-5 hours, during which you can enjoy breathtaking views of the magnificent Great Rift Valley.", "text": "You have the choice to reach the camp either by air or by road. If you choose to travel by air, flights  are  from  Wilson  Airport,  offering  a convenient 45-minute journey to Masai Mara.  On  the  other  hand,  if  you  prefer  a scenic adventure, a road safari is available, taking 4-5 hours, during which you can enjoy breathtaking views of the magnificent Great Rift Valley."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/23", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "furniture", "label": "page_footer", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 63.124, "t": 21.01271464843751, "r": 216.5605, "b": 7.610768625710193, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 19]}], "orig": "#EntumotoSafariCamp", "text": "#EntumotoSafariCamp"}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/24", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "furniture", "label": "page_footer", "prov": [{"page_no": 1, "bbox": {"l": 408.124, "t": 29.847714648437545, "r": 543.049, "b": 16.44576862571023, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 16]}], "orig": "www.entumoto.com", "text": "www.entumoto.com"}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/25", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 17.4287, "t": 805.1607146484375, "r": 138.5615, "b": 790.8653055575285, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 13]}], "orig": "GUESTS SAFETY", "text": "GUESTS SAFETY", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/26", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 17.8926, "t": 770.0565146484375, "r": 284.88399999999996, "b": 662.4234947620736, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 328]}], "orig": "Entumoto is an intimate, tented camp, designed to provide for your total comfort and the incredible sensation of being a part of this great  African  wilderness  -  the  open  sky,  the sounds and smells of the bush and its wildlife is all in high security, day and night, provided by Maasai warriors, askaris and armed rangers.", "text": "Entumoto is an intimate, tented camp, designed to provide for your total comfort and the incredible sensation of being a part of this great  African  wilderness  -  the  open  sky,  the sounds and smells of the bush and its wildlife is all in high security, day and night, provided by Maasai warriors, askaris and armed rangers."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/27", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 17.8926, "t": 642.0325146484373, "r": 284.8761999999999, "b": 534.3994947620733, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 302]}], "orig": "The excitement of being in the heart of Africa, no fences at all and open to the far horizons isolated  space!  For  the  safety  of  our  guests; after  sunset,  all  our  guests  are  escorted  by askaris through camp. We are on high altitude of 1,800 Ft and we do not have malaria mosquitos in camp.", "text": "The excitement of being in the heart of Africa, no fences at all and open to the far horizons isolated  space!  For  the  safety  of  our  guests; after  sunset,  all  our  guests  are  escorted  by askaris through camp. We are on high altitude of 1,800 Ft and we do not have malaria mosquitos in camp."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/28", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 21.4355, "t": 514.0938146484375, "r": 124.68510000000002, "b": 499.79840555752844, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 11]}], "orig": "GUEST AREAS", "text": "GUEST AREAS", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/29", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 17.4287, "t": 488.6951146484375, "r": 284.4175, "b": 317.05009476207397, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 488]}], "orig": "The  main  guest  areas,  shaded  by  a  dense multilayered canvas, consist of a sitting area, library and verandas with views of the endless gamefilled Mara plains. Beautifully hand-crafted artifacts, fine antiques, lavish sofas, books and  candlelight  will  transport  guests  back  to the heyday of the romantic classic safari. Why not  try  a  classic  safari  drink,  local  beer  or refreshing  sodas?  A  unique  feature  is  the tree-shaded swimming pool with a View of the Mara.", "text": "The  main  guest  areas,  shaded  by  a  dense multilayered canvas, consist of a sitting area, library and verandas with views of the endless gamefilled Mara plains. Beautifully hand-crafted artifacts, fine antiques, lavish sofas, books and  candlelight  will  transport  guests  back  to the heyday of the romantic classic safari. Why not  try  a  classic  safari  drink,  local  beer  or refreshing  sodas?  A  unique  feature  is  the tree-shaded swimming pool with a View of the Mara."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/30", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 22.9619, "t": 302.2608146484374, "r": 85.3715, "b": 287.96540555752836, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 7]}], "orig": "SAFARIS", "text": "SAFARIS", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/31", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "text", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 17.4287, "t": 274.3602146484375, "r": 284.41619999999995, "b": 150.72419476207403, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 336]}], "orig": "You can enjoy flexible scheduled game-drives in  open  gameviewing  vehicles.  Night  game drives  on  the  camp's  conservancy,  guided nature walks with a Maasai naturalist, Maasai community visits and lectures, sundowners at a  location  offering  spectacular  views  across the  Mara.  Hot  air  ballooning  at  an  additional cost.", "text": "You can enjoy flexible scheduled game-drives in  open  gameviewing  vehicles.  Night  game drives  on  the  camp's  conservancy,  guided nature walks with a Maasai naturalist, Maasai community visits and lectures, sundowners at a  location  offering  spectacular  views  across the  Mara.  Hot  air  ballooning  at  an  additional cost."}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/32", "parent": {"$ref": "#/body"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "section_header", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 318.6519, "t": 804.3736146484375, "r": 498.4535000000001, "b": 790.0782055575285, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 19]}], "orig": "GENERAL INFORMATION", "text": "GENERAL INFORMATION", "level": 1}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/33", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/1"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 339.7661, "t": 769.5415146484376, "r": 572.1573000000001, "b": 762.393810102983, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 61]}], "orig": "Number of Tents in Main Camp 4 Family Suites, 5 Double /Twins", "text": "Number of Tents in Main Camp 4 Family Suites, 5 Double /Twins", "enumerated": false, "marker": ""}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/34", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/1"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 339.76610000000005, "t": 755.5415146484376, "r": 576.0973000000001, "b": 748.393810102983, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 65]}], "orig": "Number of beds in Entumoto Toto - 2 family tents, 3 doubles/twins", "text": "Number of beds in Entumoto Toto - 2 family tents, 3 doubles/twins", "enumerated": false, "marker": ""}, {"self_ref": "#/texts/35", "parent": {"$ref": "#/groups/1"}, "children": [], "content_layer": "body", "label": "list_item", "prov": [{"page_no": 2, "bbox": {"l": 339.76610000000005, "t": 741.5415146484376, "r": 492.8653000000001, "b": 734.393810102983, "coord_origin": "BOTTOMLEFT"}, "charspan": [0, 38]}], "orig": "Maximum Guests